cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is about depth estimation from a single image using a convolutional neural network. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach for learning the affinity matrix, which involves a deep convolutional neural network, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also mentions the use of LIDARs, which suggests that it could be relevant to robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper involves image processing and computer graphics, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves the use of state-of-the-art methods, which could suggest that it could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
